args:
Kai Yan's tenacity only grows in defeat.
But Luca's belief in a world where all can live
as one—as well as the power of a reborn
dragon—is enough to drive the villain off.
But then Notte hears a voice in her head again,
and something strange begins to happen...
Now's our chance, Luca! Let's send this\nchump back to the damn trash heap he\nclimbed down from!
We worked SO hard for that village,\nand you ruined it!
Everyone had grown so close, but you\nhurt them—hell, you KILLED them!\nI'll never forgive you for that!
Even now, you spew your ideology of\ninfirmity. Truly, it beggars belief.
The tepid harmony that you so yearn for\nwill result in depravity ere long—and\ndepravity calls forth destruction!
They judged harmony to be right and\nproper; they were contented with it.\nAnd for that, they were CULLED!
WE MUST BE UNDEFEATED!\nWE MUST BE INVINCIBLE!\nUNASSAILABLE!
Okay, how is this guy still standing?

LOOK UPON ME! LOOK!
THE SHOCK OF MY POWER PIERCES
HEAVEN AND EARTH AND PARTS THE
SEAS OF THE WORLD! HAAAAAAAAH!
DO YOU COMPREHEND NOW MY\nPERFECTION? MY PEERLESS FORM?\nTHIS IS THE APEX OF MY STRENGTH!
He's using the power of a Qilin relic on\ntop of his own highly honed strength...\nThis is going to be a problem!
D-damn... I took everything he had right\nthere, and now my legs ain't working...
Don't worry... I ain't done yet.
I can't lose, because I'm doing this for the\nfriends who helped create our village!
They went along with my dream,\nso now I'm doing it for them!
I swore to create a world that transcends\nrace and borders...
And I won't let ANYONE stop me!
It's Jeanne d'Arc! But not like I've\never seen her before...
Luca, in honor of the pure mana that\nemanates from your most radiant soul,\nI grant unto you a great boon.
Oh man, I feel...I feel AMAZING!\nStand back, everybody!
Y-you were supposed to be weak...\nHow have you become so STRONG?!
All signs of hostile activity have ceased.\n ▷Yeah, looks like he's gone.◁
Mascula's sword ain't meant\nfor taking lives, after all.
▷I'm so happy to hear you say that!◁
Thanks for the boost, Jeanne d'Arc.

Thank YOU, Luca. Because I came into
contact with your feelings, it allowed me
to throw off the influence of the black
mana's fell power.
I shall raise this battle standard and pray\nthat you and your allies' journey continues\nwith the blessings of the light.
You saved my life, Luca. Thank you.
Okay, I think you've gone and thanked\nme enough for one day, man.
Enough with the formality! Friends always\nhelp friends out, remember? It's no big.
Even so, you have to let me thank you.\nYou've done so much for me, and I know\nyou'll continue to do so in the future.
So whether you like it or not...thank you.
If I say ＂you're welcome,＂ can we please\nstop going around and around with this?
Still, I can't say it feels ALL bad\nto be thanked by a pal. Ha ha ha!
Yes, this whole ＂friendship＂ thing may\nactually have some benefits I have yet\nto consider.
You appear to have surrounded yourself\nwith good and faithful companions all,\n{player_name}.
And with the blizzard clearing up,\nour journey can finally continue.
That sounds good to me. ...Sheila?\nWould you mind taking the lead again?
There's a stupid voice in my head!\nI think it's the same one as before!
What?! Dude, what do you waaaant?!
(I have something I must convey to you.\nAccept it.)
Okay, what the hey are you talking...\nWait, huh? What's going on?!
Things are running through my head...\nNo! No, stop!
Nnngh... My head...feels like it's about\nto crack open like a melon...
